Summary of Changes:
- Added ContrastGuard wrappers to 5 critical components
- Migrated hardcoded opacity/blur/radius to design tokens
- Added aria-label requirements for inputs and buttons
- Integrated useReducedMotion for animation respect
- Associated form labels with inputs using htmlFor/id
- Added error announcements with aria-live
- Integrated ContrastGuard into LiquidGlassMaterial
- Used motion tokens instead of hardcoded durations

This patch represents ~5% of the total remediation work.
Full compliance requires running automated codemods on all 354 components.

See reports/fix_plan.md for complete remediation strategy.
